Morgan Stanley adopted this new statute last week, which would have to allow him to diversify his activities but he does pass under the authority of the Federal Reserve.
Their alliance with MUFG also confirms that the current financial crisis forces Wall Street’s biggest names to behave much more cautiously than before.
